|YKOThere are many civilized and not so civilized races available on DarkWind.
Players can learn about and become many of these races at the Hall of Races
in Darkwind City. Race may be changed without penalty until level 5. After
level 5, changing race will cost the same as one death. As you explore 
the lands, you may come across other Halls of Races where you may learn
about and become other races.

